{"tid":533605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平過買樓】真正上車盤　29萬美元流動豪宅","createTime":"2018-01-19T03:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:30:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00426d670c4342bd36f1d34491d7bbce04f9fd50","tid":533605,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"可能你會話，難泊位喎？如果你住紅磡、土瓜灣這些「大陸團旅遊區」，你便會知道旅遊巴係可以瘋狂亂泊的。即是如果你有一部旅遊巴，要搵位過夜其實唔難，當然，在香港要找可以充電、補給、清潔的地方很難。但在美國，大量camp site歡迎你，買部車四圍去旅行，還不用租酒店住，因為這部Jayco Embark Luxury RV就是一間迷你豪宅。<br />\n<br />\n看《非常外父揀女婿》，電影中羅拔迪尼路就有一部類似的旅遊巴。這部由Thor Industries、Spartan Specialty Vehicles製作的，以Spartan K1為基本，用上Cummins360hp柴迪引擎，車價約$29萬美元起。這些都不是重點，重點是內裝，大廳有50吋LED HDTV及音響系統，睡房大床一張外亦都有32吋LED HDTV，而且大床可以三邊上落床，好過香港住宅好多主人房。另外還有廚房、廁所浴室，當中有Whirlpool雪櫃、洗手盆、花灑等設備，一定好過住劏房。選配裝備中，還可以裝上洗衣乾衣機！幾日唔落車都冇問題！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180119/large/sub5501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180119%2Flarge%2Fsub5501.jpg&h=b8fca0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180119/large/sub5502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180119%2Flarge%2Fsub5502.jpg&h=3673a71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設有輕觸屏操控裝置，能調校車內燈光及溫度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180119/large/sub5503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180119%2Flarge%2Fsub5503.jpg&h=fad9a780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睡房有大床一張，大過香港很多住宅的主人房。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180119/large/sub5504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180119%2Flarge%2Fsub5504.jpg&h=f01cae99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了車廂外，車外也有電視，方便停車露營燒嘢食。"},{"pid":"d12490fc838702bcc359f113edd87d01dedc731e","tid":533605,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"我都諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198e1666edb1b1a6ff9b078bb90c789de693f50f","tid":533605,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"二百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf17e943c9367ee71f0b6fbcd8848e9d8c5334a","tid":533605,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5DL9xIRFXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_5DL9xIRFXo&d=gOWvjm7v2wDT3Waua6LgiMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ababe000\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5DL9xIRFXo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門某個蚊型盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-I9dNfPPj2Vc/WD7lCNbpbAI/AAAAAAAAfiA/IJpmJ97Bqd8S0Es6aturxGiTlgXEU3TOgCLcB/s640/1480501004_e720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-I9dNfPPj2Vc%2FWD7lCNbpbAI%2FAAAAAAAAfiA%2FIJpmJ97Bqd8S0Es6aturxGiTlgXEU3TOgCLcB%2Fs640%2F1480501004_e720.jpg&h=0dca4afb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3717ec9975517f7192536d6f0ab2c83648ad3fc","tid":533605,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"香港攞唔到牌<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"f4304cde5c92765a33bfe9c22b46688a8e83fcbe","tid":533605,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"就算香港比你泊比你渣,<br />\n呢架野咁張揚,<br />\n點樣先至可以防止比人打劫?<br />\n要請多個看更?"},{"pid":"4e81ec36bd53f4ce97dd0972e6cc5b6e258ac0ff","tid":533605,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"揾到車位泊先講"}